A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Forest Conservation Act – Linear Projects – Alteration
3 FOR the purpose of altering the definition of “linear project” under the Forest Conservation
4 Act to exclude a project for a new transmission line or new distribution line
5 constructed on or after a certain date; and generally relating to tree removal and
6 replacement by electric companies.
